abstract: Until now, it was clearly unpopular with the public. Now it’s hard to predict.
snippet: Until now, it was clearly unpopular with the public. Now it’s hard to predict.
lead_paragraph: A majority of Americans have long opposed impeaching President Trump. Whether that will change, and what happens if it doesn’t, are some of many factors that will shape the political consequences for both parties.

lead_paragraph: Talk to Rudy Giuliani, President Trump instructed — “highly respected man,” “very capable guy,” the best.

abstract: The reconstruction of call between the two leaders becomes a flash point in the evolving fight over impeachment.
snippet: The reconstruction of call between the two leaders becomes a flash point in the evolving fight over impeachment.
lead_paragraph: President Trump repeatedly pressured Ukraine’s leader to investigate leading Democrats as “a favor” to him during a telephone call last summer in which the two discussed the former Soviet republic’s need for more American financial aid to counter Russian aggression.

abstract: The American and British leaders meet their nemesis. It’s called the law.
snippet: The American and British leaders meet their nemesis. It’s called the law.
lead_paragraph: To see them together in New York, the two charlatans, after all their nationalist-revival shenanigans, encountering the quiet force of the law was an exquisite thing. I am not sure I have ever experienced Schadenfreude in purer form.

headline_main: Trump and Johnson on the Brink

abstract: It is far worse than we could have imagined.
snippet: It is far worse than we could have imagined.
lead_paragraph: Facing growing momentum behind a full House impeachment inquiry, President Trump evidently concluded that releasing a memorandum of his phone call on July 25 with President Volodymyr Zelensky of Ukraine would quiet the investigative fervor. He could not have been more wrong.

headline_main: Trump Has Just One Plan for Victory

abstract: The president and the Democrats may be girding for a constitutional clash, but their campaigns are working to capitalize on the moment with fund-raising appeals.
snippet: The president and the Democrats may be girding for a constitutional clash, but their campaigns are working to capitalize on the moment with fund-raising appeals.
lead_paragraph: The breathless text message from President Trump and his campaign landed soon after Speaker Nancy Pelosi announced a formal impeachment inquiry: “I need you on my Impeachment Defense Team.”
